more citrusy. I then doubled the vegetables as I wanted to make quite a few meals and added three fresh red chillis.
All worked OK, fairly spicey but would add a couple more bell peppers in future.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-873661"><a id="comment-873661"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">suzlovescake</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 2nd Sep, 2015</div> </header><div class="comment__rating-and-report-wrapper"><div class="comment__rating"><div class="rate-widget rate-widget-fivestar clear-block rate-processed"><div class="fivestar-bbcgoodfood"><div class="clearfix fivestar-widget-static fivestar-widget-static-vote fivestar-widget-static-5"><div class="star star-1 star-odd star-first"><span class="on">2.55</span></div><div class="star star-2 star-even"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-3 star-odd"><span class="on"></span></div><div class="star star-4 star-even"><span class="off"></span></div><div class="star star-5 star-odd star-last"><span class="off"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__text"><div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Made the rice part of this dish with Lorraine pascal's recipe for piri piri chicken instead of using a bottled sauce. Added chopped red chilli and Cayenne pepper to the rice in addition, based on previous reviews of this being bland, and it turned out really well.</div></div></div></div> </article></div></div><div><div id="comment-wrapper-807436"><a id="comment-807436"></a><article class="comment"> <header class="comment__header"><div class="comment__author-picture"> <span class="comment__author-picture--no-login"></span></div><div class="comment__author-name"> <span class="username">ma baker</span></div><div class="comment__date"> 27th Oct, 2014</div> </header><div class="comm